vote.title: A public hearing to receive comments and to approve an ordinance granting a request to change the name of a portion of Grady Niblo Road, between Spur 408 Service Road and Kiwanis Road, to “Sharrock Road” - NC223-003 - Financing: New street blades to be prepared and paid for by the City of Dallas (see Fiscal Information for potential future costs)
